#: ../../manual/modeling/surfaces/selecting.rst:4
msgid "Selecting"
msgstr "选择"

#: ../../manual/modeling/surfaces/selecting.rst:6
msgid ""
"Surface selection in *Edit Mode* is very similar to :doc:`NURBS curve selection </modeling/curves/editing/introduction>`. The basic tools are the same as with :doc:`meshes </modeling/meshes/selecting/introduction>`, so you can select a "
"simple control point with a :kbd:`LMB`\\ -click, add to current selection with :kbd:`Shift-LMB` clicks, :kbd:`B` order-select, and so on."
msgstr ""
"*编制模式* 里的曲面选择与 :doc:`NURBS曲线选择 </modeling/curves/editing/introduction>` 非常像. 其基本操作与 :doc:`网格 </modeling/meshes/selecting/introduction>` 相同，你可以用 :kbd:`LMB` 选择一个单一的控制点，按 :kbd:`Shift-LMB` 追加控制"
"点。 :kbd:`B` 框选，等等。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/surfaces/selecting.rst:15
msgid "Select Menu."
msgstr "选择菜单。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/surfaces/selecting.rst:19
msgid "Select Menu"
msgstr "选择菜单"

#: ../../manual/modeling/surfaces/selecting.rst:21
msgid "The *Select* menu (3D View headers) is even simpler than for curves..."
msgstr "*选择* 菜单(3D 视图中的)比曲线的更简单..."

#: ../../manual/modeling/surfaces/selecting.rst:23
msgid ""
"All these options have the same meaning and behavior as in :doc:`Object Mode </editors/3dview/object/selecting/index>` (and the specificities of *Border Select* in *Edit Mode* have already been discussed :doc:`here </modeling/meshes/"
"selecting/introduction>`)."
msgstr "所有这些选项的含义和行为都和 :doc:`物体模式 </editors/3dview/object/selecting/index>` 下相同（ *编辑模式* 下 *Border Select框选* 的特殊性已经在 :doc:`这里 </modeling/meshes/selecting/introduction>` 讨论过了）。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/surfaces/selecting.rst:34
msgid "Select Linked"
msgstr "选择关联项"

#: ../../manual/modeling/surfaces/selecting.rst:36
msgid ":kbd:`L`, :kbd:`Ctrl-L` will add to the selection the mouse cursor's nearest control point, and all the linked ones, i.e. all points belonging to the same surface."
msgstr ":kbd:`L`, :kbd:`Ctrl-L` 会添加鼠标光标最近的控制点和所有相连的点，即属于同一表面的所有点。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/surfaces/selecting.rst:41
msgid "Control Point Row"
msgstr "控制点行"

#: ../../manual/modeling/surfaces/selecting.rst:43 ../../manual/modeling/surfaces/selecting.rst:62
msgid "Reference"
msgstr "参考"

#: ../../manual/modeling/surfaces/selecting.rst
msgid "Mode:     Edit Mode"
msgstr "模式:     编辑模式"

#: ../../manual/modeling/surfaces/selecting.rst
msgid "Menu:     :menuselection:`Select --> Control Point Row`"
msgstr "菜单:     :menuselection:`选择 --> 控制点行`"

#: ../../manual/modeling/surfaces/selecting.rst
msgid "Hotkey:   :kbd:`Shift-R`"
msgstr "快捷键:   :kbd:`Shift-R`"

#: ../../manual/modeling/surfaces/selecting.rst:50
msgid ""
"This option works a bit like :ref:`edge loop selection <modeling-meshes-selecting-edge-loops>` for meshes, inasmuch it selects a whole :ref:`row <modeling-surfaces-rows-grids>` of control points, based on the active (the last selected) "
"one. The first time you press :kbd:`Shift-R`, the V-row passing through (containing) the active point will be added to the *current* selection. If you use again this shortcut, you will toggle between the U- and V-row of this point, "
"removing *everything else* from the selection."
msgstr ""
"这个选项在网格的 :ref:`边环状选择 <modeling-meshes-selecting-edge-loops>` 里可用, 因为它选择一个整体的控制点 :ref:`行 <modeling-surfaces-rows-grids>` , 基于激活的项(最后选择的). 你第一次按下 :kbd:`Shift-R`, V行通过激活的点(含)将被添加到 *"
"当前* 选择中. 如果你再次使用这个快捷方式，你会在这个点的U和V行间切换, 从选择中移除 *一切别的*。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/surfaces/selecting.rst:60
msgid "More and Less"
msgstr "扩展/缩减"

#: ../../manual/modeling/surfaces/selecting.rst
msgid "Menu:     :menuselection:`Select --> More/Less`"
msgstr "菜单:     :menuselection:`选择 --> 扩展/缩减`"

#: ../../manual/modeling/surfaces/selecting.rst
msgid "Hotkey:   :kbd:`Ctrl-NumpadPlus` / :kbd:`Ctrl-NumpadMinus`"
msgstr "快捷键:   :kbd:`Ctrl-NumpadPlus`, :kbd:`Ctrl-NumpadMinus`"

#: ../../manual/modeling/surfaces/selecting.rst:69
msgid "These two options are complementary and very similar to :doc:`those for meshes </modeling/meshes/selecting/introduction>`. Their purpose, based on current selected control points, is to reduce or enlarge this selection."
msgstr "这两个选项互补而且和 :doc:`网格里的这些 </modeling/meshes/selecting/introduction>` 非常相似. 基于当前所选的控制点，其目的在于缩小或扩大这种选择。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/surfaces/selecting.rst:73
msgid "The algorithm is the same as with meshes:"
msgstr "算法和网格的一样:"

#: ../../manual/modeling/surfaces/selecting.rst:75
msgid "More"
msgstr "扩展选择"

#: ../../manual/modeling/surfaces/selecting.rst:76
msgid "for each selected control point, select **all** its linked points (i.e. two, three or four)."
msgstr "对于每个选定的控制点, 选择和它相关联的 **全部** (即二三或四).。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/surfaces/selecting.rst:79
msgid "Less"
msgstr "缩减选择"

#: ../../manual/modeling/surfaces/selecting.rst:78
msgid "for each selected control point, if **all** points linked to this point are selected, keep it selected. For all other selected control points, de-select them."
msgstr "对于每个选定的控制点, 如果和它相关联的 **全部** 点都被选中了, 那也选中它。对于所有其他被选的控制点，取消选择他们。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/surfaces/selecting.rst:81
msgid "This implies two points:"
msgstr "这意味着两点:"

#: ../../manual/modeling/surfaces/selecting.rst:83
msgid ""
"First, when **all** control points of a surface are selected, nothing will happen (as for *Less*, all linked points are always selected, and of course, *More* cannot add any). Conversely, the same goes when no control point is selected."
msgstr "第一，当一个曲面上 **全部** 控制点都被选择了, 那么什么都不会发生的(对于 *缩减*，所有相连的点总是被选择的，当然，*扩展* 不添加任何点)。相反地，没有控制点被选时发生一样的事情。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/surfaces/selecting.rst:86
msgid "Second, these tools will never \"go outside\" of a surface (they will never \"jump\" to another surface in the same object)."
msgstr "其次，这些工具不会“跳出”曲面，（它们不会跳到同一个物体的另一个面上）。"
